{"tid":2399123,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯上場半小時就扭轉乾坤 西媒:宇宙效應","createTime":"2021-02-08T00:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T06:17:21.000Z","uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6603070e10cde44d852244280ed3778b9274984","tid":2399123,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"上場半小時，攻入1球，參與2球，美斯再次開啟神奇模式。<br />\n<br />\n  《每日體育報》賽後給了美斯8分的全隊最高分，評語指出：「地震效應。他的上場對對手來說幾乎具有宇宙般的效應。上場後差不多是第一個行動就勁射近門柱側得分，讓對方門將猝不及防。他拿起了進攻指揮棒，吸引了對方球員。」<br />\n<br />\n  該報還打出了「美斯是上帝」的標題，表示美斯上場之前球隊的表現證明，這位世界上最好的球員今夏不能離開，否則巴塞將會很糟糕。他只用了半個小時就讓著急的高文獲得了平靜。他上場就入球，讓對手恐慌，引領了球隊的逆轉"},{"pid":"7efa6563a0ac82751f8f3df58bd810dedde3d350","tid":2399123,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:32:30.000Z","msg":"諗起每年歐聯關鍵戰都有黑洞效應"},{"pid":"3f1b641f62cd34a569802dd07b0ba767292b7c40","tid":2399123,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qCC8WngYO-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqCC8WngYO-s&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=0106974d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qCC8WngYO-s</a>"},{"pid":"c3d78a0a8c456d82fe2728a9fd3746025e911f45","tid":2399123,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"唔係破產咩？"},{"pid":"04211252b23715d403be65399f72f1a5537521fb","tid":2399123,"uid":54344,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt3dDZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt3dDZJ.jpg&h=a25c1ea3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e92f0105a35d8e14fbd02198e3be3b704a1ede2","tid":2399123,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d78a0a8c456d82fe2728a9fd3746025e911f45","tid":2399123,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T00:33:30.000Z